snippet.title: Lil Nas X Addresses 'Call Me By Your Name' Controversy
snippet.description:
Lil Nas X reacts to Nike lawsuit over his “Satan Shoes”. Plus Amber Heard is responding to Johnny Depp fans and Kelly Clarkson is looking back at starring in that “American Idol” movie.
